Detailed Description

Dma Parameters for CAL M2M driver.

Field Documentation

uint32_t vpsissCalm2mDmaCtrlParams::bwLimit

Defines a minimum cycle count between to consecutive read requests issued by the RD DMA.

uint32_t vpsissCalm2mDmaCtrlParams::ocpTagCnt

Maximum allowed number of outstanding OCP read requests. Max value is 0xF

uint32_t vpsissCalm2mDmaCtrlParams::pixClock

Controls the data rate at which data is read from the read DMA FIFO and sent to the internal processing pipeline.
